sellerCard.oneLiner: Crafting Your Online Edge with Ecommerce Web Design and SEO Expertise
sellerCard.description:
Expert Shopify/ShopifyPlus Agency offering end-to-end eCommerce solutions for businesses and entrepreneurs. Ideal for clients seeking a hassle-free creation, support, enhancement, or migration of their online stores. We excel in eCommerce development, providing a seamless all-in-one service, including:

• High-quality, maintainable eCommerce development.
• UX strategies to boost conversion rates.
• Contemporary, captivating designs for your store.
• Advanced SEO optimization to elevate your online visibility.

description.content:
All queries are welcome, leave us a text. No strings attached.

Special discounts for the Holidays season!


We will set up your store from scratch or give it a much-needed revamp. We will set up everything from Shipping settings to store design customization, believe me you're in good hands. We will also help you set up Email Marketing automation to increase and convert sales as well as convert abandoned carts. As a Social Media expert, I will also share some tips to increase your Social media presence. We have quadrupled the sales of stores in a month by a complete revamp and marketing strategy implementation. Our impact on the stores can be verified by our previous clients, so don't take our word for it!


Why This Gig?


  • Shopify Store with Premium Professional design
  • SEO friendly store
  • Mobile, laptop & tablet friendly design
  • Shipping methods
  • Domain and SSL setup
  • Newsletter subscription pop-up
  • Creation of information pages (Terms of Service, Shipping, etc)
  • Google Analytics
  • Setup Payment Gateway
  • Marketing Guide
  • 24/7 Support
  • And Many More



Note: Sharing of email/contact details may be required as part of completing the order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will there be a language barrier for a English Speaker?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I speak really good English with perfect grammar. I guarantee that of 99% times, there will not be an issue.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you also manage ecommerce/Shopify stores?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I manage stores on monthly basis. Feel free to reach out to discuss this.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I contact you for assistance after the store is completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I offer 15 days of guidance/support after handing over the store. I can guide you with anything related to e-commerce such as your ads/ marketing plan / developing a business mindset etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you design a logo for the store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I have experience in Photoshop & will create a clean and simple branded logo for your store.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why are you underpriced?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I am from Pakistan and the conversion rate for USD is very high, so I have adjusted my prices so everyone can afford high-quality websites! And I can also make a living. My end goal is to share my experience with people from all over the world.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I able to get my sales after you complete my order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes absolutely! After I complete your order, your Shopify store will be 100% ready to make sales by doing marketing.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need from me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will need you to fill out the order requirements and provide access to the store (if you already have one) or I am a registered Shopify Partner and I can create a new store for you through my Shopify Partners account.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I contact you before placing an order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I highly encourage this as this would help me understand your needs better and I can provide guidance for free too if needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What kind of themes can we use to build the Shopify store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
We can either use free Shopify themes or licensed Envato themes, as I have an Envato subscription. If you bear the expenses, we can also use Shopify paid themes.

Please note: I do not include any paid themes or licenses in my service.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I'm a beginner, can I start Shopify Store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! It's never too late to start this. We have got success from Shopify, now it's the time for me to help you get there. Turn your business into an e-commerce giant!

reviews.comment: I was not at all hesitant to use Fiverr, even though this was my first time, because of its stellar reputation. I was a bit wary of who to choose; how ever. I looked around the site and happened upon Noor Ahmed- he offered three price ranges and his star rating was solid- so I picked him and went mid range on the pricing/ man did he deliver. I gave him almost nothing from the start and he, somehow, picked enough information from me to create an extremely professional looking website. He designed my logo, helped me name my company, he basically went above and beyond. I will continue to go back to him throughout this process as I will continue to return to Fiverr. Thank you.

I hired Noor Ahmed for a project, and he delivered the work quickly and followed the instructions as requested. While he met the brief, I found the results to lack creativity and initiative. The work was very standard, not quite polished, and therefore didn’t quite meet my expectations. However, if you're looking for someone to execute exactly what you ask for without deviation, Noor is reliable and efficient.

I could not recommended Noor and his team anymore!! He went above and beyond to cater for my website design needs and my expectations were blown out the window. If you're thinking about doing it, then Noor is your guy. Response time, receptiveness and attention to detail. Cant wait to launch!!

Noor did a phenomenal job, returned a beautiful website very quickly, and was able to adjust and add anything I wanted afterwards. I would recommend him to anyone that is looking to have their website redesigned very well at an affordable price.

Working with seller was easy, simple, everything i needed for my website he gave me in a super timely manner. If i ever need anything again website design related i will come to him. He made my website immensely better.
